<item>
            <title>[LU-8042] mkfs.lustre should set ashift=12 recordsize=1024k compression=lz4&quot; by default for new ZFS OSTs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8042</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be useful for &lt;tt&gt;mkfs.lustre&lt;/tt&gt; to set &lt;tt&gt;ashift=12&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;recordsize=1024k&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;compression=lz4&lt;/tt&gt; for new ZFS OSTs.  It doesn&apos;t make sense to do this for MDTs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="36252">LU-8042</key>
